<p>
      <hi rend="italics">Women picking olives </hi>(<rs type="artwork" ref="artwork.xml#ill_2879">F 655 / JH 1869</rs>).</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="2" xml:id="note-t-2">
                            

<p>Van Gogh must be referring to the painting <hi rend="italics">Ravine </hi>(<rs type="artwork" ref="artwork.xml#ill_2881">F 661 / JH 1871</rs>); in an earlier letter he had told Theo that it was not yet dry (<ref target="let836.xml">see letter 836</ref>).</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
